=== Passive recon overview ===
Physical/Social

Location Information
Satellite Images
Drone recon
Building layout (nfc readers, break areas, security, perimeter)

Job Information
Employees (name, job title, phone number, manager etc.) [LinkedIn, Twitter]
Pictures (badge, desk, computer photos etc.)

Build yourself a profile, know names of others, make a fake badge

Web/Host Target Validation - WHOIS, nslookup, dnsrecon
Finding subdomains - Google Fu, dig, nmap, bluto, crt.sh, sublister etc.
Fingerprinting - nmap, wappalyzer, whatweb, builtwith, netcat
Data breaches - HaveIBeenPwned, breach parse
